      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，FRAME和SDK都在Pezkuwi子图外面。FRAME是底层框架，跟Runtime是双向的虚线依赖。SDK是开发者工具库，跟Node也是虚线连接。都不是强依赖，用虚线表示比较合适。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRAME",
        "PezkuwiRuntime",
        "PezkuwiSDK",
        "PezkuwiNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
